
colormap(2)                    Scilab Function                    colormap(2)
NAME
  colormap - Using colors in Scilab

DESCRIPTION
  Colormaps.

EXAMPLE
  m=228;
  n = fix(3/8*m);
  r = [(1:n)'/n; ones(m-n,1)];
  g = [zeros(n,1); (1:n)'/n; ones(m-2*n,1)];
  b = [zeros(2*n,1); (1:m-2*n)'/(m-2*n)];
  h = [r g b];
  xset('colormap',h);
  plot3d1()

SEE ALSO
  xget, xset
